<h2>Yahoo is shutting down Delicious</h2>
<div class="endpost"><!-- testing -->
	<p class="intro">… And &#8220;merging&#8221; Upcoming to make way for exciting, can&#8217;t-miss features like Yahoo! Babel Fish, Yahoo! Deals, and Yahoo! Avatars.</p>
<p>Photo: <a href="http://yfrog.com/f/h3z89p/">yfrog.com/f/h3z89p/</a>.</p>
<p>Hat tip: <a href="http://twitter.com/#!/waxpancake/status/15483488237002752">Andy Baio</a>.</p>
<p>Burn, Alexandria, burn!</p>
