<div class="timestamp">
	<h3><a href="http://www.zeldman.com/2010/12/15/an-event-apart-gives-thanks/">15 Dec 2010</a> 7 am eastern</h3>
</div>


<h2>An Event Apart Gives Thanks</h2>
<div class="endpost"><!-- testing -->
	<p><a href="http://aneventapart.com/news/2010/12/07/an-event-apart-gives-thanks/"><img class="inset" src='http://www.zeldman.com/wp-content/aea-logo.gif' alt='' /></a></p>
<p class="intro">To thank you and the universe for five brilliant, sold-out shows in 2010, we’ve partnered with Network for Good to donate $5,000 to Computers for Youth (CFY), a non-profit foundation that brings computing and educational resources into the homes of children who wouldn’t otherwise have these advantages. <a href="http://aneventapart.com/news/2010/12/07/an-event-apart-gives-thanks/">Read more</a>.</p>
<div class='sociable'><div><span class='sociable-tagline'></span></div><ul><li><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank"  href="http://delicious.com/post?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zeldman.com%2F2010%2F12%2F15%2Fan-event-apart-gives-thanks%2F&amp;title=An%20Event%20Apart%20Gives%20Thanks&amp;notes=%0D%0A%0D%0ATo%20thank%20you%20and%20the%20universe%20for%20five%20brilliant%2C%20sold-out%20shows%20in%202010%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20partnered%20with%20Network%20for%20Good%20to%20donate%20%245%2C000%20to%20Computers%20for%20Youth%20%28CFY%29%2C%20a%20non-profit%20foundation%20that%20brings%20computing%20and%20educational%20resources%20into%20the%20home" ><img src="http://www.zeldman.com/wp-content/plugins/sociable-30/images/default/16/delicious.png" class="sociable-img sociable-hovers" title="del.icio.us" alt="del.icio.us" /></a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank"  href="http://digg.com/submit?phase=2&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zeldman.com%2F2010%2F12%2F15%2Fan-event-apart-gives-thanks%2F&amp;title=An%20Event%20Apart%20Gives%20Thanks&amp;bodytext=%0D%0A%0D%0ATo%20thank%20you%20and%20the%20universe%20for%20five%20brilliant%2C%20sold-out%20shows%20in%202010%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20partnered%20with%20Network%20for%20Good%20to%20donate%20%245%2C000%20to%20Computers%20for%20Youth%20%28CFY%29%2C%20a%20non-profit%20foundation%20that%20brings%20computing%20and%20educational%20resources%20into%20the%20home" ><img src="http://www.zeldman.com/wp-content/plugins/sociable-30/images/default/16/digg.png" class="sociable-img sociable-hovers" title="Digg" alt="Digg" /></a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank"  href="http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zeldman.com%2F2010%2F12%2F15%2Fan-event-apart-gives-thanks%2F&amp;t=An%20Event%20Apart%20Gives%20Thanks" ><img src="http://www.zeldman.com/wp-content/plugins/sociable-30/images/default/16/facebook.png" class="sociable-img sociable-hovers" title="Facebook" alt="Facebook" /></a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank"  href="http://